snippet.title: Gaming Couples Gaming Setup! Matching DXRacer Chairs, BenQ Monitors, Razr Naga & More!
snippet.description:
Couples gaming setup! This video shows off all the cool stuff Amber and I have for our matching setup! For me, I have an IBuyPower Desktop, Razr Naga Mouse, Corsair Keyboard, Astro A50 Headset, Logitech C920 Webcam! We both share a Blue Yeti for the microphone for our twitch stream, and we both have matching DXRacer chairs, and matching desk. Amber just got a Gaming Laptop by Dell from BestBuy today and it runs WoW on the highest settings so we are pretty happy about that because we got a good deal on it! Oh and she has some sweet Razr ManOWar headphones!
